Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.54,0:00:51.53,Default,Wom,0000,0000,0000,,Locally grown cucumbers! {cucumbers, technically but w/e}{firstly, you can't grow a pickle and secondly, why not use cucumber instead of pickle?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.79,0:00:55.69,Default,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,And you know what, mommy? They said I was the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.65,0:00:53.77,Default-alt,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.69,0:00:57.53,Default,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Better than all the other kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.53,0:01:02.79,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Marry me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.79,0:01:04.04,Default,Wom,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.77,0:01:08.70,Default,Bal,0000,0000,0000,,Is this your first time in the capital, Rygart? {alt; big city}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.70,0:01:11.65,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I came here once when I was just a squirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.65,0:01:13.05,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,My dad brought me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.01,0:01:15.57,Default,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:16.93,Default,Bal,0000,0000,0000,,Rygart!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.42,0:01:18.64,Default,Bal,0000,0000,0000,,Rygart!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.34,0:01:20.39,Default,Bal,0000,0000,0000,,Can you move?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.25,0:01:46.45,Default,Io,0000,0000,0000,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.88,0:01:51.04,Default,Io,0000,0000,0000,,Fall back, men.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.74,0:02:06.77,Default,Bal,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Rygart?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.69,0:02:09.39,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.39,0:02:10.61,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, pops?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:20.50,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say? I can't hear you. {speaking to girghe, not baldr}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.67,0:02:24.49,Default,Bal,0000,0000,0000,,Were heading back to Binonten.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.49,0:02:28.10,Default,Bal,0000,0000,0000,,The three of you, watch our backs and keep an eye out! Don't get caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.10,0:02:29.11,Default,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.20,0:02:38.73,Default,Gua,0000,0000,0000,,Refugees coming from the north, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.73,0:02:39.80,Default,Gua,0000,0000,0000,,Let them in!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.66,0:02:42.29,Default,Gua,0000,0000,0000,,Standby until the escort troops return!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.29,0:02:45.09,Default,Gua,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure the palace is sufficiently guarded!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.09,0:02:47.30,Default,Gua,0000,0000,0000,,A riot's broken out at the central shelter!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.99,0:02:50.06,Default,Gua,0000,0000,0000,,I thought they'd appointed a spokesman!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:53.00,Default,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,How goes the boarding at the harbor?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:54.83,Default,Min,0000,0000,0000,,Where has King Hodr gone to?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.83,0:02:58.82,Default,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,The troops are gathering in the town square! Where are the generals?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.35,0:03:01.25,Default,Min,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find His Majesty anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.25,0:03:03.45,Default,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Relocate to the eastern garrison!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.09,0:03:08.70,Default,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! What's the Guard doing!?
